txt.en: 'New arrivals should meet with the magistrate. You can find Magistrate Zebulo at the crest of Jax Phanâl, in the heart of the city. From the stable-master, travel through the north gate and turn right through the central arch. Take the stairs up to the crest of the outpost.'

New arrivals must meet with the magistrate. The magistrate is at the crest of Jax Phanâl north of the stable-master, beyond the first right through the arch and at the top of the stairs. Visit Magistrate Zebulo now.
As a new arrival, you should seek the counsel of the outpost's magistrate.

'New arrivals should meet with the magistrate. You can find Magistrate Zebulo at the crest of Jax Phanâl, in the heart of the city. From the stable-master, travel through the north gate and turn right through the central arch. Take the stairs up to the crest of the outpost.'
Speak with Magistrate Zebulo at the crest of Jax Phanâl
'A visitor from abroad, eh? Your arrival is most fortuitous. Let us speak plainly.'
